<h2>About This Page:</h2>

<!-- Note: the b and a tags below have nameless end tags in the .if file: -->
The <b><a href="/&agentName;/">&agentName;</></b> agent is intended as a
demonstration and testbed for the PIA's InterForm markup language and its
formatter/interpretor.  This page is intended for testing and experimentation;
it is expected that each user will make a customized version.

<dl>
  <dt> <b>Note:</b>
  <dd> You are <em>strongly</em> encouraged to make a copy of this page
       in the &agentName; subdirectory of your personal Agents directory
       (<code><a href="/My/Agents/">&usrDIR;/Agents</a></code>).  You can do
       this with the command:
</dl>
<pre>
cp &piaDIR;/Agents/&agentName;/&fileName; &usrDIR;/Agents/&agentName;/&fileName
</pre>
<hr>

<actor tag=demo quoted=1 dscr="show both CONTENT and its value">
  <protect-result markup><get name=content></protect-result> <b>=&gt;</b> 
<expand><get name=content></expand>
</actor>

<dl>
  <dt> <demo><set entity name=foo><ul><li>1<li>2</ul></set></demo><br>
       <demo><repeat list="&foo;">&li;--</repeat></demo>
  <dd> 
  <dt> <demo><set entity name=foo><li>1<li>2</set></demo><br>
       <demo><repeat list="&foo;">&li;--</repeat></demo>
  <dd> 
</dl>

<pre><demo><read file="~/.login"></demo></pre>
<pre><demo><read file="~/.pia"></demo></pre>
<pre><demo><read directory match="^[A-Z].*[^~]$" tag=ol file="~/.pia"></demo></pre>
